{"tid":1387561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對戰術有啲意見","createTime":"2019-07-30T14:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:22:29.000Z","uid":66108,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6fbf291a13376b6e733d2e83d3ccc1b76feb9e70","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>希望大家比少少耐性睇完</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先我發誓 我絕對絕對絕對尊重前線 我亦都好珍惜每一個義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到啲義士 拉嘅拉 傷嘅傷 走上前線嘅人愈來愈少 戰力愈來愈少 情況愈黎愈危險<br />\n<br />\n其實對方同我地實力真係差好遠<br />\n係 我地有不停進化 但有冇諗過 其實慢慢地我地嘅思想偏向左 一定要同警犬對峙<br />\n我唔係話呢個方向係錯 只係 我地有本錢升級防具 點解冇時間諗下仲有咩不同方向嘅路可以行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家記唔記得有義仕係政總出面圍鼠王芬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最尾條八婆咩都做唔到 敗走搭的士都失敗<br />\n<br />\n其實呢個方法真係可行<br />\n一班人快閃 冇單一目標 佢地想叫狗都難<br />\n即使叫到 大家已經走哂 實行大家所講 be water<br />\n呢個方法同樣唔會一次就成功 但可以令我地嘅敵人<span style=\"color: red;\">咩都做唔到 變地底泥 變過街老鼠</span> 亦都可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>減低風險</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實 成唔成功真係好睇人數 上次捉20幾個義士 今次40幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地仲有可以犧牲幾多個義士?<br />\n日後只會愈來愈多義士被捕<br />\n為免再有人犧牲 我地一定勇武得黎 好好保護自己 珍惜係戰場上同我地並肩嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求求各位好好考慮下呢個方法 我亦都唔係第一個提出呢類意見<br />\n義士唔能夠無限消耗 勇武但可以保護自己 係一個非常好嘅方法黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe93071ef92761252e5453c3f05b1fbecb69587","tid":1387561,"uid":293012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:31:32.000Z","msg":"試下呢個夢啦～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n組織全民玩快閃！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc728741f73d85b24ec626995412d3c0eb7adfb6","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:32:20.000Z","msg":"不分化 不篤灰 不割席<br />\n大家加油<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n我愛香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f7f401efb46233db47402e7fb69887cc8333a1","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:32:31.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4b2c6da08e5ea4217993d5a3199a8f3aec97ce51","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"推推推 唔好再比義士犧牲"},{"pid":"39cb9133cf8a4b1f8325850d7568b98fa288f9e4","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:36:49.000Z","msg":"推呀屌"},{"pid":"f175c159fae0f87342400c1228bf5a07b499998e","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:37:38.000Z","msg":"跪求注意"},{"pid":"d27d9d7829347cdc7cc844b6db9e441a4ac02202","tid":1387561,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89d2380ed2bbad2335112cf9f5bdbc44ee2d8a2","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:38:58.000Z","msg":"推呀 有冇人見到呀"},{"pid":"6dc20540740e0f8f9344e1769836d5a079b03118","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"去完葵涌睇下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求求大家 義士一個都不能少呀"},{"pid":"77507b238b78305aa88a798916d6dfc70ec24b68","tid":1387561,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike"