aces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比埋個屎忽你 求望下呢個post"},{"pid":"6fdff8db27797a3fe576481cac9175f7ee8ed798","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"自己推自己"},{"pid":"36a9c32e44e646b56df5e3b3325e50d3e7cabed6","tid":1387561,"uid":278071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:39:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"066173a93f2ea5fd3c22213595c127d9786186ba","tid":1387561,"uid":278071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"唔好再有犧牲！！"},{"pid":"1f95349003609494b7facc73abdfe5cb8e7287e0","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:40:24.000Z","msg":"求手足大大力推我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaff7599dbd480b34a43b766c7d9d14376dc4f58","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:43:04.000Z","msg":"呢個方法可以加大警犬壓力 好彩嘅話仲可以收到某啲生物會吞槍自殺嘅喜訊<br />\n大家考慮下好唔好"},{"pid":"f54bd477a53741b94aafed4a38f9fee9e5c7e4aa","tid":1387561,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}